annotations:
  - {"kind":"agent","id":"agent-b2976c318ce84ae43d4283b9cfb92aa8","agentId":"ce1e8a00-b1b7-4f99-9a0c-6f4ad4f0468c","agentSessionId":"992c5328-6640-43c2-9aa3-8249a3f59cf2","body":"## Lit sidebar layout\n\n`MessagesApp` is the browser-side custom element loaded by `apps/messages/index.ts`. In its normal mode it composes the Agents pane and annotation viewer with a keyboard- and pointer-resizable separator; prompt composition, agent history, and an expanded annotation view replace that layout as takeovers.\n\nIt receives the host state in `applyHostMessage`, keeps only transient UI state locally, and emits typed user actions back to the provider.\n","createdAt":"2026-07-21T12:05:48.890Z","anchor":{"line":753,"text":"\trender() {","before":["\t\t\tlayout.style.gridTemplateRows = `minmax(0, ${this.agentPanePercent}fr) 8px minmax(0, ${100 - this.agentPanePercent}fr)`;","\t\t}","\t}"],"after":["\t\tif (this.prompt !== undefined) {","\t\t\treturn this.renderComposerTakeover(this.prompt);","\t\t}"]},"userAnnotation":{"annotationId":"7d61322c-9ab7-4ca3-860b-78f99980e0ef","file":"packages/editor/src/webviews/messages/messages.ts","line":14}}
